Here are the prompts I used to develop video player.
I used Cursor to develop this software.
Hello, kindly build a video player using java.
Kindly set the color for video player area to black. 
Add a file menu on the top of video player and provide general file menu options including open video option. Remove the open video and stop button.
Add a scroll bar to the bottom of the video player. 
Plot the play button in the center of the bottom pane. Turn this button into a toggle pause play button and remove the pause button.
